\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh no, well he was always in the house and - apart from visiting, going to meetings you see. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 So he'd be out in the evening a lot probably?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Did your father attend any clubs or pubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 No. He didn't. But he associated 
with men of clubs and pubs - in the council work, and he would go on deputations and so on to London with them, and they all said that he was a help to them. We must be careful, Mr Salmon's with us - that sort of thing, but he would join with them, he wou
ld take whatever he wanted I suppose, but - he didn't join in their -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 He was with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Not of them, yes, exactly.
