\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Did your father or mother belong to any savings clubs, they used to have a funeral club and a sick club years ago?
