\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 How did you get on with your brothers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Very well. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Did you feel particularly close to one or the other of them?
