\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 A different relationship really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Different relationship, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Did you feel as close to both of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 As a child who did you play with?
