\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 How much would you have when you had it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh I haven't a clue now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 You mean if you wanted to go somewhere you'd just ask would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes, if we were going somewhere - we'd be given money, you know. But how much - about five shillings I should think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What would you spend the money on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh, sweets. And - I remember buying a torch, I remember my first torch. That sort of thing, but not - we did
n't have a lot of money to spend, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Did you have it every week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 No, not a regular thing, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Did anyone outside the home help your mother to look after her house or family?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Well yes, this Miss - Hodges.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Any relatives coming?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes, they'd come on special occasions. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Because you had a very busy household didn't you really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 
We did. Yes. And we had a friend who - who was a cook in a house - Gwr Mawr you know and she would - come over now - if we had an anniversa
ry preacher Doctor Williams, Bryn Siencyn and - and Gwalchmai to make something special. Yes. Yes. Yes. She was from Cardigan and she made - spent a lot - all her spare time with us. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 She was just a friend, she wasn't actually a relative was she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Would any neighbours help at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 No. Don't think neighbours came.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 If your mother was ill or confined to bed how did she manage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Well her sister would come - from Llantwit. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 You did mention that when your little brother was born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes, she was there then. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 No one else would come would they, only that one sister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes. And - we had a friend - a - a minister's daughter, the Baptist minister's daughter, and she came to help quite a lo
t. Yes. She was paid for it. There was need for it. Yes. She's still alive, eighty-one. Yes. She helped quite a lot, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Did your parents have any relatives living nearby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Maesteg was quite a distance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh yes. Yes, Llantwit Fardre my mother's people were the nearest. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 That's fairly near isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Six miles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Six miles from here, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Maesteg's much further isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh yes. And my father then - his people had - left Maesteg, he - w
as the last of that - generation, but they had - connections there and cousins.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Your father's brother in Cardiff?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes. And another one in Newport who then moved to Morriston, Congegational, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 There were no other relatives nearby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 How much did they see of their relatives, you used to see a fair amount of the one in Cardiff?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes, yes, not a great deal of the others. Occasionally. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 The aunt in Llantwit Fardre?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh yes, we were there often, and my mother's brother lived there, so my first cousins then we were all - we saw quite a lot of each other.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Would you go there or would they come here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Both. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Did your parents have friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh yes. Lots of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 You mentioned that one lady who was very friendly with your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh yes. Yes. But we had other friends too. Chiefly our friends were ministers. And their wives and families. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Where would your parents see them?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 They'd come and visit us. We'd visit them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Did they share the same friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 No. Well - actual friends yes, but they had - acquaintances in connection with their churches, and we had them - with ours.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Would your mother and father have the same friends, or would your mother have her friends and your father have his friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh no, the same friends. Yes. Family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Your mother did have that one particular friend of her own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh yes. Yes. Yes. And she had another one in Llantwit Fardre. Mrs Reece the Coroner's wife, great friends, they talked together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 So she had the two friends of her own,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Would your father have any friends like that of his own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Not so much I would say. Only ministerial friends again you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 You said your mother was very chatty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh very. Yes. Very sociable. Yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Where would she see her friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh at home. They would come home. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Where would your father meet his friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Well I}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1967813\charrsid3897122  think chiefly in the fraternal}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122  and so on you know, yes, and the - the local ministers, they spent lots of their time in our home. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Would they be offered anything to eat or drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh always. - Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Would they come on any particular days or occasions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Day time. We had two bachelor
 ministers, and they spent most of their time - most evenings with us. Food and - yes. Lovely life. Yes. My father had a billiard table put into one of the spare rooms we had in another house, and he and they, they would play these games there and - jolly
 you know, the conversation was great. Yes. Mm.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Would you say that the friends invited in were your mother's friends or your father's friends or friends of both of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Both of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Would they call in casually without an invitation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh dear, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What about neighbours, would they call in without an invitation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Not so much. No. There were one or two who would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Did your parents ever go out to visit friends like that or to their neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Not to their neighbours but to special friends that they had.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 
People often tell us that in those days they made their own amusements, what do you think your parents did when they got together with their friends? You mentioned your father used to play billiards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes. But that was only in our house. Talk chiefly, yes. And music where my mother was concerned of course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Would she go to someone's house and have a musical evening there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes, in one especially. She would go. And then - yes, she - oh to a few of
 them. But to - to help them with their music chiefly. It would be a musical evening helping them. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 It would be music and games with your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Many people divide society into different social classes or groups, in that time befo
re 1918 did you think of some people belonging to one class and some to another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes. Definitely.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Could you tell me what the different ones were then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Well, there were the chapel going people and the non-chapel going - as far as I was con
cerned. And there were the - professional and the non-professional. But that didn't make any difference to our attitude towards them. But we - we did realize there was a difference.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 You did mention earlier the lower class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Who would you call those?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Well, in my estimation it was those who drank and so on. You know?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Which class or group would you say you belonged to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Middle. Yes. There were as we called the crachach. And there were the very - not so much working class as 
- morally different, and I thought we came in between the two.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What sort of people belonged to the same class as yourself would you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Well the chapel people. Really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 All the chapel people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes. The very respectable what they did or -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What sort of people belonged to the other classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Pretty rough.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Who would you call the crachach?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Well now we had - a Judge, Gwilliam Williams, now his family, and - the doctors we thought were - the schoolmaster I felt we were on 
more or less the same level, but - the doctor was special, and - the aristocrats, they lived in very big houses around here, we considered they were - crachach. Church of England.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes. Most of them. And - they had cars. One or two fam
ilies had phaetons. Do you know, the - the low and they went in those and we thought they were very important people. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 The chapel people were in the middle group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 The middle. Yes, like us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Would you put all the church people in the other class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 
Oh no. No. But there were one or two who - who were outstanding, they were moneyed people to begin with, they dressed differently, and - they were more English too, which we thought then was a little bit grand. I'm sorry to say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Why was that I wonder?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 
I don't know. They were - well educated some of them. They weren't Welsh and they - they spoke with - what we'd call now a - an Oxford accent sort of, some of them had been.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Were they factory owners or colliery owners? Or were they landed gentry?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes, landed gentry most of them round.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 It's quite a country area?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes. Now Tal-Y-Garn, a big mansion up here, Crochta a big - mansion over there. Yes, landed gentry I would say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What about the colliery managers and colliery owners?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 
Well - we were friendly with the - the one colliery manager I knew near, they weren't any collieries actually in Llantrisant. But we were friendly with him but we considered they were a bit - above the - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Then you said there was a lower class, who would you put in that class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 
Well - some of them were colliers, tin plate workers, but then - there were also colliers and tin plate workers - in the middle class. But from my point of view it - it - it was their way of living
. That - divided them. And their - moral tone, as I say, drinking and gambling and - racing with dogs, you know, that sort of thing, I - I thought they were - but my father could mix with them all. He was -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Can you remember being brought up to treat people of one sort differently from people of another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 No. Never -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Were you ever told to curtsey?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 To whom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 To Lady Williams Miskin, Judge Williams' wife. We weren't told at home but she demanded it - when she came into scho
ol or if we met her on the street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Miskin Manor is quite near?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes. That was where she lived you see. Yes, oh yes, we had to curtsey to her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Did you ever have to show respect in some other way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 No. On the other hand she came to our ho
me, and was very friendly with my - mother and father, and she would always bring things with her. And we thought she was great for doing that, whether it was patronage or what I don't know but we were very glad of - what she - yes. Was a perfect lady, on
e of the Aberpergwms.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Was there anyone then described as a real lady or a real gentleman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 
Yes. Well she was. Yes. Judge Gwilliam Williams, Sir Rhys Williams father wasn't, as they said then, of such a high class, but she was one of the Aberperwgms.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Can you remember anyone else being described as a real gentleman of a real lady?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 
Lady Price - Fothergill Price at Hensul Castle. She was another one we thought very high, but she again - my father and she were very - friendly. Well don't misunderstand that statement.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Were they church people or chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes, church. Judge Gwilliam Williams, chapel, in our little Welsh chapel in Miskin. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Was there anyone you called sir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 No, we called the schoolmaster sir.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Anyone you called master or madam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Do you remember anyone showing respect to your parents in any way, like touching their cap?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes. Yes, to my mother always. The people - the men round, they respected her greatly. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 In the district then who were considered the most important people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 The doctor. Minister. Schoolmaster. The police - too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 So your father would have been considered one of the important people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh yes. Yes. And the vicar.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Why were they considered important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Well people came to them for advice and I think they got - help from them. I think that was it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Did you come into contact with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 With?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 With these people who were considered important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Because of being in a minister's house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 And you say they used to come to the house a lot?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What about the shopkeepers then, who did they associate with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh well, with us. They were members of our churches you see, round. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What about the clergy, who would they associate with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Well with their own members - mostly I think, but they associated with us too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Would they associate with your father?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh yes, they visited us. Yes. Canon Griffiths I remember so wel
l. And any new vicar or curate who came to the district was always - invited. I remember one - vicar, young wife coming, and we were about to have supper and they started eating and my father said grace, and he had a great sense of humour, he - he - he wa
s
 - very amused at it, and the - the lady had started eating, she put her knife and fork down, and she said, afterwards, oh Mr Salmon, I'm so sorry. We haven't been in this line long. My father said, doesn't matter a bit Mrs Evans, oh she was lovely, and h
er husband - hadn't been in this line long. And my father wasn't a bit - \{BLANK\} in that silly sense you know. Well he - he did say grace you know. Yes. indeed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What about the teachers then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh yes, we were very friendly with the teachers. And an
y new teacher who came to the district, no matter what denomination or any denomination, there was always invited. One teacher came from Llanelly to the Baptist, she's still a great friend of mine, she's eighty-three years of age now and it's been a life 
l
ong friendship, a wonderful singer, therefore they had something in common with my mother you know, and then - if my mother was going away or - wanted - if there was a private meeting, someone coming, I would go to her digs to tea with her and my brother.
 They helped each other in that way. Lovely person. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What about the farmers then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh very friendly with the farmers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Who would they associate with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Well, with the farming community - on the whole, but - very friendly with us. And my father was a great friend of the farmers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What about employers, were there any employers round here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 No, not really. Only the shopkeepers you see and - and theirs were - business of their own really, didn't employ a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 There wouldn't be a works here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 No, there weren't, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What sort of people would you say went to the church? You did say just now that you thought the English people on the whole?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 To the Church of England? Oh yes. Yes. They were -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 The upper class you seemed to think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 
Yes. Yes. More of the - Conservatives. Yes. Yes. Well there were all classes there of course. All - political parties and a cross section. But - chiefly it was considered a bit more crachach to go to church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What about the chapel, what sort of people would go to chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh - the - the lower classes as they were called then. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Where you lived then did all the people in the working class or lower class have the same standard of living or would you say there were 
different groups?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 
There were different groups, yes. It depended on - on what they earned, quite a bit, they way they lived you see, and there were some - as I say some chapel people, some - non-chapel, there were lots of Irish people in the district,
 and they were very indifferent toward - there was no Roman Catholic church you see, therefore -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 I was going to ask you if there was a Catholic church here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 No there wasn't. The nearest was Treforest, after some years, yes, but now there is one in the district. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 So really they were rather without a shepherd?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 They were, they were neglected, but - my father was friendly with them and they would come to him for advice on many things. Yes. Yes.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 It was difficult for them probably?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 It was. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Do you think that one group in the lower class would feel superior to the rest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 
Yes, I think so. Now the railway people for instance were very - methodical tidy people always, and I think they felt - or we felt perhaps - that 
they were more responsible - than the others, they were very good living people, and kept their houses tidy and - took a pride in everything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 You often hear people saying, oh yes, he worked on the railway?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes. There's a precision belonging to them. Yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 It was like that was it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh it was definitely, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Do you think some of the families were thought of then as rough and others as respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes. Definitely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Do you remember a distinction of this kind between craftsmen and labourers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Not so very much. No, I - I - I don't think so. It would depend on the labourers again you see. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 You mean on the way they were living?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 You think that was the difference really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 I think so, that would - that was the - the demarcation - yes, the way they lived.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Did your mother and father have the same attitude to people in different classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 They respected everybody.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Do you think your mother saw herself as belonging to a particular social class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Was it possible in that time to move from one class to another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Not very easily. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Do you remember anyone who did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 No, I don't think so. No, I can't think of anyone really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Do you remember seeing a policeman around where you lived as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What did you think of him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh I thought he was - to be feared in a way. And yet I felt - well he was looking after us.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Were you ever sort of threatened with, I'll tell the policeman, your mother never said anything like that did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 You weren't frightened of him that way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh not a bit, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 How do you think he treated the people then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 He was pretty strict I think if need be. The people resp
ected him. And children did. If the policeman walked down things changed if they were up to something.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Why do you think that was, why did you yourself feel a little fear of him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh well - fear of going to prison I suppose or being - reprimanded or -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Was your home rented?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes. The first one was, but they were bought afterwards each one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 The one we were talking about?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Ty'n y Berllan. That was rented at first and then bought. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Did you see anything of your landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes, quite a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What did you feel about him as a landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh, he didn't do all we wanted him-to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Do you remember feeling that your parents had a struggle to make ends meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Well I felt there wasn't a lot of spare money but - we were never made to feel that we were - poor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What did you think about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 
I was perfectly satisfied. I did feel sometimes I saw girls being dressed - oh exotically, but now when I look back - I think well - our sense of values was the - better.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 It didn't make any difference to your father if he was ill or out of work, because he was the minister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 He wasn't really out of work ever was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 No, and he wasn't often ill. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 So you didn't have to get help, he was one of the Guardians wasn't he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 When there was someone in the district whom the people disapproved of very strongly was there any special way in which they showed it?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 I never heard - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Nothing like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Never. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Were you given lessons by one of your parents, a tutor or a governess?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 My mother helped us quite a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 You had singing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Music lessons, singing lessons, and she'd help us with homework and so on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 How old were you when you first went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Five I should think, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What time in the morning did you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 
We must have gone very early because we had such a long walk. Excepting when we - later we went in this - governess car with these people. Oh I should think about half past eight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What time would you come back? Would you go all day to start with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh yes. Yes. I should think we must have finished about four.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 You said you had about three miles to go?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes. That -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Was that the first school when you were five?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 You had to walk all that way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What sort of school was it, was it boys and girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Mixed. Mixed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 It wasn't a church school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 It was a board school was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 You went with your uncle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 And your brother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 You don't remember how long it took you to get there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh well - walking it would surely take us three}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1967813\charrsid3897122  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 quarters of an hour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 And you had your midday meal there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What did you think of school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 I enjoyed it. Yes. I had a wonderful head }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1967813\charrsid3897122 \endash }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122  head}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1967813\charrsid3897122 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 
teacher in the infants school. Well she was in charge, uncle was the head, and - she died - almost ninety about two years ago, well she was such a lady and so perfect that - she was my ideal - lady. She was a wonderful person. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 You thought of her as a real lady then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes, absolutely. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Did the teachers emphasise certain things as important in life, in that school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh - I don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Manners, tidiness?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Punctuality?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Ways of speaking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 If you did something the teachers disapproved of what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 I think - they had the cane.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Girls as well as boys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes. Yes. 
I remember having the cane - later in another school for talking too much. My friend and I were always talking. And the headmaster said, I can imagine you two over the garden fence, he was very fond of us, bit if the teacher sent us to him for the cane he
 had to give it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 So you'd have the cane?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 For talking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes, yes. Talking too much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Did your parents show an interest in your schoolwork?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Did they ask you what you did at school?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Would they visit the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Would they meet the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 
They knew them. Yes. Well now in the other school - when I was about - seven I moved to another school at Talbot. And we knew the headmaster there and we knew the teachers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 How long did it take you to get there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh, ten minutes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Walk?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Who would you go with there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 My brother, and friends round. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Did you take your lunch there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes, but we went over to a little shop where they cooked meals for children, and we paid for them there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 So you had your meal out then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What did you think of that school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh I liked it very much. Yes. Only they did use the cane 'cos we talked too much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What about the teachers there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Very good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 In the school you went to did the children come from similar types of home to your own or not?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh, a cross section really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Did the teachers single out some children for different treatment from the others.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 I don't think so. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Were there any gangs or groups in the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 No, we all played together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What about those children in the rough part you said?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Ah yes, well I was never in that school, that was the church school at the top. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 There weren't many going to the same school as you were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Not from that area, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Then you went on to the school at Talbot?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What about the children there, did they come from similar types of home to your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Did your parents ever visit that school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Were there any gangs or groups in that school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Did the teachers single out children for different treatment from the others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 I don't think so, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Were there any children who were left out of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 
No, I'll tell you what I do remember about those days, there were many dirty children. Dirty heads and things like that you know, and the nurse used to come and see, and they were singled out in t
hat way, to be examined, and that worried - me a lot. Yes. That they were different.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Would you play with those children then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes. Oh we all played with them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 It didn't make any difference?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 It made difference to my - state sometimes. But they were lovely children, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Because the conditions were different then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh yes. Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Did you go on to another school afterwards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes, I went to the High School then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Where was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Cowanridge. Yes we went by train. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Q}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12912552\charrsid3897122 u}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 
ite a way isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Quite a way, we walked down to the station, that took us about half an hour. And then by train.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 How old were you when you went there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Ten.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What time would you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 About nine I think the train went in the morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What time did you come back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12912552\charrsid3897122 Five}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 ish.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What kind of school was that, a mixed school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 No, a girls school Cowanbridge - High School, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Was it a state school, a board school?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Mm - yes. Girls High School. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 There were boarders there as well weren't there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes, there were. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Who would go with you then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh many local girls. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 How long did it take you to get there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh about - twenty minutes by train I should think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 And ten minutes walk to the train?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What about the other end then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh the school was quite near the station. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What about your midday meal there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 We had it in school. I did. Some brought sandwiches you know but I had the dinner there, with the boarders.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What did you think of that school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 
Oh great. Rather strict. Yes. You had a headmistress, Mrs Forrester who was a minister's widow, very high moral code - we - and - the way we dressed, we - had an orde
r mark if you went out without gloves, that sort of - thing you know, and - had to behave well on the train. I was made a train perfect I remember, look after other girls and - oh dear. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 What would happen there if you did something the teachers disapproved of?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Order marks we had. Yes. And lectures of course from the head teacher.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Did your parents ever visit that school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Prize distribution day you know, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Did they ask you what you did at school?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh yes. They were interested, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Would they meet the teachers from that school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 
Some of them, yes, some of them visited my home you know, there were connections, family connections with the teacher perhaps and my father or the minister of that teacher would - write and then we'd invite them up, that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Did the teachers single out some children for different treatment from the others at the High School?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 I don't think so, there was a certain element - at one time - they spoke of the children from
 Pontyclun up as the children of the hills, which they disliked very much. You know, up Tonyrefail way and so on, and they were lovely people but - there was that - Cowbridge was a little - bit crachach, they thought they were, beginning of the Vale of Gl
amorgan down. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Were there any gangs or groups in the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Did they group, the children from the -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Well the hills, yes, they stuck together, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 There were groups really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Well I suppose there were, yes, that sort of group. But not gangs as gangsters, as they are now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 But groups of girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Oh yes. I would say so, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Would you all from Llantrisant stick together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Yes. More or less.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 You wouldn't mix so much with the others would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 
Not so much. And yet there wasn't a great difference. The boarders we felt were a little bit superior to us. We felt it. I don't know whether - there was a little bit of - difference.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 Did you go on to another school after that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 No. I went to college from there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 How old were you when you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7152858 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 
Actually I did a year's student teaching - from sixteen to seventeen, we - we taught for two days - and went to school for the rest of the week.
