on? Well yes I did. I went - to all the theatres and plays I could and concerts. The best of everything, and - shopping, London and so on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4344133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12469020\charrsid3897122 You went out in the evening a lot?
